name: Treasurer Colleen Davis
tweet: I testified on the Senate floor yesterday in support of H.B. 145, creating new personal income tax deductions for people saving with DE529 Education Savings Plan accounts or Delaware-sponsored ABLE accounts. name: Treasurer Colleen Davis
tweet: The State Senate will vote on H.B. 145 tomorrow (Tuesday). Sponsored by Rep. Krista Griffith, the bill creates deductions of up to $1,000 for contributions to a DE529 account and up to $5,000 for contributions to  a Delaware-sponsored ABLE account.  https://t.co/IFbINCtY4h
